House Bill 4112
Sponsored by Representative HUDSON, Senator WEBER, Representatives MCINTIRE, DOBSON, OWENS,
WRIGHT, Senators FREDERICK, NERON MISSLIN; Representatives ANDERSEN, BUNCH, CHOTZEN,
DIEHL, EDWARDS, ELMER, GAMBA, GOMBERG, GRAYBER, HARBICK, HELFRICH, HELM, ISADORE,
